summary: Real Madrid nogometni klub s najvećim prihodom na svijetu  Real Madrid zamijenio je Manchester United na prvom mjestu...
caption:
Real Madrid nogometni klub s najvećim prihodom na svijetu

Real Madrid zamijenio je Manchester United na prvom mjestu najbogatijih nogometnih klubova na svijetu nakon što je u sezoni 2017/18. zabilježio rekordne prihode, objavila je revizorska kuća Deloitte. Prema podacima revizorske kuće Deloitte Real je prošle sezone ukupno zaradio 750,9 milijuna eura. Deloitte je također objavio podatak da je prvih dvadeset klubova zajedno zaradilo rekordnih 8,3 milijarde eura, što je šest posto više od sezone prije. Cijeli članak možete pročitati na: tportal.hr Foto: Pixabay

title: NFF Awards to hold on April 1
body:
NFF Awards to hold on April 1

Another award for Nigeria’s football family will hold on April 1, 2019.

﻿The Amaju Pinnick led Nigeria Football Federation (NFF)﻿ have confirmed that the second NFF Awards will take place on Monday, April 1.

The inaugural NFF Awards was held on Monday, February 19 at the Grand Ballroom of the Eko Hotel and Suites, Victoria Island in Lagos.

summary: Research: This Girl Can – what about you? Really catchy music in this extremely well-done ad. I love how the audio editing in...
caption:
Research: This Girl Can – what about you?

Really catchy music in this extremely well-done ad. I love how the audio editing in the whole advert, especially how some specific sounds are isolated from the environment (heavy breathing) and the music goes quiet. The prompt for the music to start at the beginning is absolute genius.

summary: Research: Here to Create Change, adidas #CreatorsUnite I love how straightforward this ad is. Switching through different...
caption:
Research: Here to Create Change, adidas #CreatorsUnite

I love how straightforward this ad is. Switching through different sports, the only audible sounds are actions and the background track. The background music works well as the tempo makes the different shots flow well together. I’m not sure about the audio at the end resembling a stadium though, I don’t feel it’s necessary and it seems a bit brutally interrupted.
